# Free Stamp PNG Generator

Create transparent stamp PNG images online instantly — no login required.

If you need to generate a digital stamp, remove background from a stamp image, or create a transparent PNG seal, this tool provides a simple and fast solution.

---

## 🚀 Try It Online

👉 https://cynicalkim.com/sign_and_stamp_generator/

---

## 🔥 What You Can Do

- Generate stamp PNG images online
- Create electronic stamps (personal / company seal)
- Remove background from stamp images
- Convert scanned stamp images to transparent PNG
- Download high-quality stamp images instantly

---

## 🧰 Common Use Cases

- Add stamp to PDF documents
- Create digital signatures for contracts
- Generate company seal or official stamp
- Convert paper stamp to digital format

